016package com.exoreaction.xorcery.jsonapi.client;
017
018import jakarta.ws.rs.WebApplicationException;
019import jakarta.ws.rs.core.Response;
020
021import java.util.function.Consumer;
022
023/**
024 * Helper for handling Responses.
025 */
026public interface ResponseHandler
027        extends Consumer<Response> {
028    @Override
029    default void accept(Response response) {
030        int status = response.getStatus();
031        if (status < 200) {
032            status1xx(response);
033        } else if (status < 300) {
034            status2xx(response);
035        } else if (status < 400) {
036            status3xx(response);
037        } else if (status < 500) {
038            status4xx(response);
039        } else if (status < 600) {
040            status5xx(response);
041        } else {
042            statusOther(response);
043        }
044    }
045
046    default void status1xx(Response response) {
047        switch (response.getStatus()) {
048            case 100 -> status100(response);
049            case 101 -> status101(response);
050            case 102 -> status102(response);
051            default -> unknown(response);
052        }
053    }
054
055    default void status100(Response response) {
056        unknown(response);
057    }
058
059    default void status101(Response response) {
060        unknown(response);
061    }
062
063    default void status102(Response response) {
064        unknown(response);
065    }
066
067    default void status2xx(Response response) {
068        System.out.println(Response.Status.OK.getStatusCode());
069        switch (response.getStatus()) {
070            case 200 -> status200(response);
071            case 201 -> status201(response);
072            case 202 -> status202(response);
073            case 203 -> status203(response);
074            case 204 -> status204(response);
075            case 205 -> status205(response);
076            case 206 -> status206(response);
077            case 207 -> status207(response);
078            default -> unknown(response);
079        }
080    }
081
082    default void status200(Response response) {
083        unknown(response);
084    }
085
086    default void status201(Response response) {
087        unknown(response);
088    }
089
090    default void status202(Response response) {
091        unknown(response);
092    }
093
094    default void status203(Response response) {
095        unknown(response);
096    }
097
098    default void status204(Response response) {
099        unknown(response);
100    }
101
102    default void status205(Response response) {
103        unknown(response);
104    }
105
106    default void status206(Response response) {
107        unknown(response);
108    }
109
110    default void status207(Response response) {
111        unknown(response);
112    }
113
114
115    default void status3xx(Response response) {
116        switch (response.getStatus()) {
117            case 300 -> status300(response);
118            case 301 -> status301(response);
119            case 302 -> status302(response);
120            case 303 -> status303(response);
121            case 304 -> status304(response);
122            case 305 -> status305(response);
123            case 307 -> status307(response);
124            case 308 -> status308(response);
125            default -> unknown(response);
126        }
127    }
128
129    default void status300(Response response) {
130        unknown(response);
131    }
132
133    default void status301(Response response) {
134        unknown(response);
135    }
136
137    default void status302(Response response) {
138        unknown(response);
139    }
140
141    default void status303(Response response) {
142        unknown(response);
143    }
144
145    default void status304(Response response) {
146        unknown(response);
147    }
148
149    default void status305(Response response) {
150        unknown(response);
151    }
152
153    default void status307(Response response) {
154        unknown(response);
155    }
156
157    default void status308(Response response) {
158        unknown(response);
159    }
160
161    default void status4xx(Response response) {
162        switch (response.getStatus()) {
163            case 400 -> status400(response);
164            case 401 -> status401(response);
165            case 402 -> status402(response);
166            case 403 -> status403(response);
167            case 404 -> status404(response);
168            case 405 -> status405(response);
169            case 406 -> status406(response);
170            case 407 -> status407(response);
171            case 408 -> status408(response);
172            case 409 -> status409(response);
173            case 410 -> status410(response);
174            case 411 -> status411(response);
175            case 412 -> status412(response);
176            case 413 -> status413(response);
177            case 414 -> status414(response);
178            case 415 -> status415(response);
179            case 416 -> status416(response);
180            case 417 -> status417(response);
181            case 418 -> status418(response);
182            case 420 -> status420(response);
183            case 421 -> status421(response);
184            case 422 -> status422(response);
185            case 423 -> status423(response);
186            case 424 -> status424(response);
187            case 426 -> status426(response);
188            case 428 -> status428(response);
189            case 429 -> status429(response);
190            case 431 -> status431(response);
191            case 451 -> status451(response);
192            default -> unknown(response);
193        }
194    }
195
196    default void status400(Response response) {
197        unknown(response);
198    }
199
200    default void status401(Response response) {
201        unknown(response);
202    }
203
204    default void status402(Response response) {
205        unknown(response);
206    }

209        unknown(response);
210    }

213        unknown(response);
214    }

313    default void status5xx(Response response) {
314        switch (response.getStatus()) {
315            case 500 -> status500(response);
316            case 501 -> status501(response);
317            case 502 -> status502(response);
318            case 503 -> status503(response);
319            case 504 -> status504(response);
320            case 505 -> status505(response);
321            case 507 -> status507(response);
322            case 508 -> status508(response);
323            case 510 -> status510(response);
324            case 511 -> status511(response);
325            default -> unknown(response);
326        }
327
328    }
329
330    default void status500(Response response) {
331        unknown(response);
332    }
333
334    default void status501(Response response) {
335        unknown(response);
336    }
337
338    default void status502(Response response) {
339        unknown(response);
340    }

342    default void status503(Response response) {

370    default void statusOther(Response response) {
371        unknown(response);
372    }
373
374    default void unknown(Response response) {
375        error(new WebApplicationException(response.getStatusInfo().getReasonPhrase(), response.getStatus()));
376    }
377
378    default void error(Throwable throwable) {
379    }
